node.text:
Experience 4th of July on Hornblower's INFINITY Yacht during the biggest ever planned NYC's Fireworks Show! All ages welcome! Bring your whole family!

💣 House music floor:
@andrewbesada_dj @juniorperom @djthbueno 

Latin/ Hip Hop floor:
@djpablonyc @xermane @djmluv 

Rain? No problem, there are two large indoor dance floors!!

Climb aboard the Infinity for a 4TH of July Night on Manhattan waters filled with music, delicious meals and Skyline views!

Dancing under the Fireworks on the East River! Yes we are on the largest & most luxurious yacht in the NYC Harbor!
